    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.92.5581.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Oahutanais makalii gen. et sp. n., holotype female: A pereopod- 1; B pereopod- 2; C pereopod- 3; D pereopod- 4; E pereopod- 5: F pereopod- 6; G uropod; H pectinate seta. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
